*Help*==jv_display_commands
*Hello*|*Hi*|*SALUT*==say "Hi, how are you today $username?"
*Am Okay*==say "Thats great to  hear"
*How are you*==say "Don’t worry about me, am a robot, get it? haha!"
*Cholera*==say "Welcome to Solve Cholera services, what can we do today?"
>*Sick*==say "Please check if you have any of these symptoms"
>>*Running Stomach*==say "Please call this number 0800-CHOLERA"
>>*Vomiting*==say "Please call this number 0800-CHOLERA“
>*I just wanna learn*|*learn*|*learning*==say "Okay, here is a quick information about cholera, ensure to check this link for documented data"
*COMMENT*APPELLE*==say "Je m'appelle $trigger"
*MERCI*==say "De rien"
*AU REVOIR*|*BYE*==say "Au revoir $username"; jv_exit
*WHAT ARE YOU DOING*==say "Chilling"
ANNULE*|TERMINE*==bypass=false; say "Ok"
ENCORE*==jv_repeat_last_command
*TEST*==say "Ca fonctionne!"
*VERSION*==say "Je suis en version $jv_version"
*REPETE (*) ET (*)==say "(1) (2)"
*CA VA*==say "Très bien et toi ça va?"
>*OUI*==say "ravi de l'entendre"
>*NON*==say "j'en suis navré"
